---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const today = new Date();
const formattedDate = `${today.toLocaleString('en-US', { month: 'long' })} ${today.getDate()}, ${today.getFullYear()}`;
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | RecycleOldTech.com"
  description="Learn how RecycleOldTech.com collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit our website."
>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
          
          <div class="inline-block bg-accent-50 text-accent-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md mb-6">
            <p class="m-0"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {formattedDate}</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">At <strong class="text-accent-600">RecycleOldTech.com</strong>, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">We may collect certain non-personally identifiable information about your visit, including:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
          <li>Referring website or source</li>
          <li>Location data (at the city/region level)</li>
          <li>Device type and operating system</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-md border-l-4 border-accent-500">We do <strong class="text-accent-800">not</strong> collect any personally identifiable information unless you choose to provide it via a form submission (e.g., location search or contact form).</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">We use the collected information to:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>Improve the performance and functionality of our website</li>
          <li>Understand user behavior and traffic patterns</li>
          <li>Help connect users with certified electronics recycling centers</li>
          <li>Monitor and analyze the effectiveness of our content and tools</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">3. Analytics and Tracking</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">RecycleOldTech.com uses the following third-party tools:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong class="text-accent-700">Google Analytics</strong> and/or <strong class="text-accent-700">Vercel Analytics</strong> to monitor website traffic and usage</li>
          <li><strong class="text-accent-700">Google AdSense</strong> to serve ads that may be relevant to your interests</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">These tools may set cookies or collect usage data to help us better understand our visitors. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">4. Google AdSense and Cookies</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">We use <strong class="text-accent-700">Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements. Google may use cookies or device identifiers to personalize ads and track performance.</p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">You can learn more about how Google uses data here:<br />
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-800 underline">https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a></p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
          <li>Request deletion or correction of your data</li>
          <li>Opt out of data collection (via browser tools or ad opt-out links)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">To make such a request, please <a href="/contact" class="text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-800 font-medium">contact us</a>.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, please note that no online transmission or storage system is 100% secure.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">RecycleOldTech.com may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new effective date.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out through our:</p>
        
        <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-accent-500 transition-colors">
            Contact Page
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />
        
        <p class="text-center text-lg font-medium text-accent-700 bg-accent-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-8"><strong>Thank you for visiting RecycleOldTech.com and for doing your part to support responsible e-waste recycling.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</Layout> 
